{"tid":1872871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"莎莎旗下港澳區21間分店暫停營業","createTime":"2020-02-10T09:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T08:05:18.000Z","uid":273901,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38ef489c483065e271d59351d3f20b9153ac198a","tid":1872871,"uid":273901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"【有線財經】莎莎旗下港澳區21間分店暫停營業。<br />\n莎莎表示，因應疫情蔓延，為保障員工及顧客安全，加上考慮到現時消費需求低，港澳區21間分店暫停營業，直至另行通知。<br />\n集團將根據業務需求，靈活部署人手，將受影響分店的員工安排至其他分店工作。同時，採用分更制形式，減少值班員工數目，控制成本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c53d30fbc0201bbf17ca98e979547ff6814ec1","tid":1872871,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"又要請小鳳姐出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小鳳姐呢排真係忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9733af9abc27317a0296ffcc6664c8a4a3ad150f","tid":1872871,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63565c67a69f3fb461d6a896faf930aa586745ce","tid":1872871,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"藍絲美夢成新<br />\n<br />\n經濟衰退<br />\n<br />\n衰過03年沙士果陣"},{"pid":"19b9aa2a7bf82d1b027e14959d486f21d5fa171f","tid":1872871,"uid":208940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"剩係贏馬獎金已經無撚敵啦"},{"pid":"9232e5cc8cdd4974374651b1e3d13a4ab5fd2763